<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Demande d'actualisation - {{ devis.numeroDevis }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12 0%, #e67e22 100%);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-header .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .alert-box strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .info-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-section h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #495057;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6c757d;
            min-width: 140px;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #212529;
        }
        .message-section {
            background-color: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .message-section h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #004085;
        }
        .message-content {
            color: #004085;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            color: white !important;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0056b3 0%, #003d82 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .cta-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #dee2e6;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .badge-warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .badge-info {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="email-header">
            <div class="icon">🔔</div>
            <h1>Demande d'actualisation de devis</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="email-body">
            <div class="alert-box">
                <strong>⚠️ Action requise</strong>
                Un client a demandé {% if isExpired %}une actualisation{% else %}une modification{% endif %} pour le devis <strong>{{ devis.numeroDevis }}</strong>
            </div>

            <!-- Informations du devis -->
            <div class="info-section">
                <h2>📄 Informations du devis</h2>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Numéro :</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><strong>{{ devis.numeroDevis }}</strong></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Client :</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{ devis.client ? devis.client.nomComplet : 'Non défini' }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Montant TTC :</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><strong>{{ devis.totalTtc|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</strong></div>
                </div>
                {% if devis.dateValidite %}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Date de validité :</div>
                    <div class="info-value">
                        {{ devis.dateValidite|date('d/m/Y') }}
                        {% if isExpired %}
                        <span class="badge badge-warning">Expiré</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Statut actuel :</div>
                    <div class="info-value">
                        <span class="badge badge-info">{{ devis.statut|upper }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Informations du demandeur -->
            <div class="info-section">
                <h2>👤 Demandeur</h2>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Nom :</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{ clientNom }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Email :</div>
                    <div class="info-value"><a href="mailto:{{ clientEmail }}" style="color: #007bff;">{{ clientEmail }}</a></div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <div class="info-label">Date demande :</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{ dateDemande|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Message du client -->
            {% if message %}
            <div class="message-section">
                <h3>💬 Message du client</h3>
                <div class="message-content">{{ message }}</div>
            </div>
            {% else %}
            <div class="message-section">
                <h3>💬 Message du client</h3>
                <div class="message-content" style="font-style: normal; color: #6c757d;">Aucun message spécifique fourni par le client.</div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <!-- Call to action -->
            <div class="cta-container">
                <a href="{{ lienEdition }}" class="cta-button">
                    📝 Modifier le devis maintenant
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px;">
                Le statut du devis a été automatiquement changé en <strong>"Actualisation demandée"</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
                <strong>TechnoProd ERP</strong><br>
                Système de gestion commerciale
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px;">
                Cet email a été généré automatiquement suite à une demande client.<br>
                Pour toute question, contactez le support technique.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
